-- MOVES-Houlihan Lokey names Richard Lee as a managing director
-- By Yashaswini Swamynathan in Bengaluru
-- Wed Dec 10, 2014 12:04PM EST
-- None



Dec 10 (Reuters) - Investment bank Houlihan Lokey appointed Richard Lee as a managing director to its dispute resolution and financial expert opinions team within the financial advisory services division.

Lee, who most recently Lee served as a partner at Deloitte Financial Advisory Services, will be based in New York.